w version in action visit <a href=\'http://techozoic.clark-technet.com/\'>here</a>.  This version has many enhancements including: </p>\n<ul>\n<li>Switched to Options Framework Option Panel</li>\n<li>Using Custom Header functions</li>\n<li>Removed Cufon support (strictly using Google Fonts)</li>\n<li>Removed support for navigation menus other than built-in menus</li>\n<li>Added support for status, quotes, and aside post formats</li>\n<li>Various CSS3 styling changes, new calendar style, comment form styling, social media icons</li>\n<li>Fixed widget bug not saving options</li>\n<li>Added status update widget</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\'http://techozoic.clark-technet.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/techozoic-fluid.zip\'><img src=\"http://techozoic.clark-technet.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/zip_icon_box_.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Techozoic Fluid\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-213\" /></a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"http://techozoic.clark-technet.com/2012/01/new-version-2-0/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Next Version News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://