">Bank of the West</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"http://www.friendsofpir.com\" target=\"_self\">Friends of Portland International Raceway</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </font></td></tr>\r\n        <tr><td><p><font size=\"2\" face=\"Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">\r\n        The board and staff wish to thank all of you who have made recent donations of money and/or time. If you haven\'t donated lately please do so, your contributions are crucial to keeping the doors open, and remember they are tax deductible!</font></p>\r\n            <a href=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/PDFs/NPTLBirthdayPartyPoster_2011.pdf\"><img src=\"/img/announcements/NPTLBirthdayPartyPoster_2011_medPrev.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"713\" border=\"0\"></img></a></td></tr>\r\n\r\n      </table>", "Sponsors", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "20-revision-3", "", "", "2012-10-04 14:33:56", "2012-10-04 22:03:56", "", "20", "http://northportlandtoollibrary.org/uncategorized/20-revision-3/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("49", "1", "2012-10-04 14:34:09", "2012-10-04 22:04:09", "<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Never used a power tool before? Tired of listening to that leaky faucet? Not only does the North Portland Tool Library have tools, we also sponsor hands-on workshops to help you learn to use those tools more effectively. The workshops are free and will be designed and run by skilled individuals from the community or partner organizations.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height=\"248\"><!-- Upcomming Workshops //-->\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #aa0066;\">Upcoming Workshops:</span></strong>\r\n\r\nPlease consider becoming a \"fan\" of the North Portland Tool Library on Facebook. We have found it easiest to communicate our upcoming workshops there. We\'ll also try to post them up here and on the calendar, but we found Facebook to be the most effective for getting the word out. It\'s also an easy way for you to stay connected with the most up to date information from us.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/North-Portland-Tool-Library/129473544092\" target=\"_self\">http://www.facebook.com/pages/North-Portland-Tool-Library/129473544092</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"left\"><strong>Pictures from our very first \"Basic Skills\" workshop</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/NPTL_Images/WS_1_29_05_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/NPTL_Images/WS_1_29_05_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\">Workshop instructor Laura Dalton blathers on about the slide miter saw and safe use.</span></span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\">North Portland resident Pamela Jeanne lets the chips fly under Laura\'s watchful eye.</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/NPTL_Images/WS_1_29_05_3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/NPTL_Images/WS_1_29_05_4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"166\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<td><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\">North Portland resident Lorenzo Carmona practices sinking sheet rock screws to the perfect depth with the cordless drill.</span></span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small;\">Sisters and NP residents Zannah (left) and Jennifer Martell (center) experience the thrills of reciprocating saw demolition with the assistance of Oregon Tradeswomen instructor Dawn Jones (right).</span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">Are you skilled in the building trades and interested in sharing your knowledge with others? Or maybe you have a great idea for a workshop. If so, we would love to hear from you. Our primary goal is to give residents of North Portland the information they need, so community input is crucial.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nContact us with\r\nyour input.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>", "Workshops", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "24-revision-3", "", "", "2012-10-04 14:34:09", "2012-10-04 22:04:09", "", "24", "http://northportlandtoollibrary.org/uncategorized/24-revision-3/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("69", "1", "2012-12-17 21:48:52", "2012-12-18 05:18:52", "<img src=\"http://www.northportlandtoollibrary.org/NPTL_Images/Firehouse.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nThe North Portland Tool Library (NPTL) is a community resource dedicated to building community and fostering sustainability by providing residents with tools and the power to use them. We loan a wide variety of tools to community members <strong>free of charge</strong>. The NPTL benefits North Portland residents by reducing the costs of maintaining and improving the places in which we live, work, and play. The NTPL helps support diverse, livable neighborhoods and fosters community pride.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Paypal\" href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=R7MM3FQWEFJ72\" target=\"_blank\"><input type=\"image\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" /></a>\r\n<img src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">\r\n<div>Dear NPTL Member,                    December 2012</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Greetings! We hope this correspondence finds you in good spirits and good health.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The North Portland Tool Library has seen unprecedented growth in 2012. As we near a whopping 4,000 members, it becomes even more important that we keep our tools in tip-top shape. Our goal is to continue to maintain regular hours, secure high-quality tools for the North Portland community and offer suggestions for proper tool selection at every check-out.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>To do that, we need you.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>This December, we’re asking each member for a $30 contribution.  Your contribution fills any of these critical needs.</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>More than two hours of salary to keep the doors open</li>\r\n	<li>A month of electricity</li>\r\n	<li>A month of heat</li>\r\n	<li>Three circular saw blades</li>\r\n	<li>A drill</li>\r\n	<li>Hedge trimmer sharpening</li>\r\n	<li>New brushes for two sanders</li>\r\n	<li>A heavy-duty 50-foot extension cord</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Donations may be made by cash or check. Please make checks out to North Portland Community Works, and include your NPTL membership number on the memo line. You can drop your donation off during normal NPTL hours OR drop it in the mail to the address listed above.  Or new just for you this December donations can be made online to Paypal.</div>\r\n<div><a title=\"Paypal\" href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=R7MM3FQWEFJ72\" target=\"_blank\"><input type=\"image\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" /></a></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>We truly appreciate your support. Your donation is tax-deductible—and it helps us keep our pledge:</div>\r\n<div>Power Tools to the People!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Sincerely,</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The NPTL Board and your friendly Tool Coordinator</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Douglas Hartman, Gerald Howard, Teri Thomas Petersen, Franny French, Preston Browning, Arolia McSwain, and Laurie Menet</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>*Please note: the Tool Library will be closed on Christmas Day, Tuesday, 12/24, and New Years Day, Tuesday, 12/31</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The North Portland Tool Library is a project of North Portland Community Works a qualified organization</div>\r\n<div>for tax exempt status under IRS Section 501(c)(3).  Tax ID: 93-1156762   Donations are tax deductible as the law allows.</div>\r\nRegistration with the Library is free to all residents of <strong>North Portland</strong> and there are no costs aside from late fees and replacement charges. Please see the <a href=\"http://northportlandtoollibrary.com/membership/\">membership</a> tab for additional details about registration and requirements.</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"></td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" width=\"400\" height=\"85\">\r\n<table width=\"93%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Become a \"fan\" of the North Portland Tool Library on Facebook. It\'s an easy way for you to stay connected with the most up to date information from us!<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/pages/North-Portland-Tool-Library/129473544092\" target=\"_self\">http://www.facebook.com/pages/North-Portland-Tool-Library/129473544092</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>", "Tools and the Power to use them.", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "4-revision-6", "", "", "2012-12-17 21:48:52", "2012-12-18 05:18:52", "", "4", "http://northportlandtoollibrary.org/uncategorized/4-revision-6/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
